    "Moreover, the AVE of all constructs ranged from 0.744 to 0.898, which surpassed the 0.5 thresholds 83, further demonstrating convergent validity.",
    "Discriminant validity was verified through Fornell-Larcker Criterion and Heterotrait-Monotrait (HTMT) Ratio.",
